schools.name: Joseph L Bowler Sr  Elementary School

data.description:
3 BEDROOM/DEN 2 FULL BATHS open floor plan 1532 square feet. Large kitchen with lots of counter space. Large master bedroom with walk-in shower, soaking tub, and walk-in closet. Guest bedroom large closet. Laundry room located off kitchen. HVAC cooling and heating. Fully fenced back yard, covered patio, covered cement RV pad with full hookups. Graveled back yard with automatic sprinkler system, outdoor kitchen. Extended 2 car garage.   Refrigerator, washer/dryer, built in microwave, stove, dish washer, reverse osmosis, water heater, and water softener are included.

 Installed in home: Fiber-optics, Smoke/Heat Detectors, Water Sensors, Smart Thermostatic, Patio Sunscreens, Window Sunscreens and Locking Security Screen Doors.
